@NODE "MedPlayse" "PlayMED plays"


          PlayMED V1 plays all MED-modules headed with MMD0 or MMD1
          with 4-channels and samples smaller then 137000 Bytes. 
          
          PlayMED V2 just like V1
          
          PlayMED V3 like V1, additionally every generation up to MMD3 with
          mix-routine for 1 to 64 channels or mix-routine for 5 to 8 channels.
          That means: All MED-modules you can create with OctaMED Sound-Studio
          V1.03c or earlier versions.


@ENDNODE
